---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Income Tax Comparison Calculator | Compare Tax Rates in Europe"
description: "Compare income tax rates across 10 European countries. See effective tax rates, social contributions, and net income for tech professionals relocating abroad."
---

{% block structuredData %}
<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "WebApplication",
  "name": "Income Tax Comparison Calculator",
  "url": "{{ site.url }}{{ page.url }}",
  "description": "{{ description }}",
  "applicationCategory": "Utility",
  "operatingSystem": "All",
  "offers": { "@type": "Offer", "price": "0", "priceCurrency": "USD" },
  "author": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "{{ site.name }}", "url": "{{ site.url }}" }
}
</script>
<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "FAQPage",
  "mainEntity": [
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Which European country has the lowest income tax for tech workers?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Bulgaria has one of the lowest flat income tax rates in Europe at 10%. However, total tax burden includes social contributions. Switzerland also offers competitive rates that vary by canton."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "How do social contributions affect my take-home pay in Europe?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Social contributions (pension, healthcare, unemployment) can add 10-22% on top of income tax. In Germany, employee social contributions are about 20% of gross salary. In the Netherlands, they're built into the tax brackets."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Does the 30% ruling in the Netherlands reduce my tax?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Yes, the Dutch 30% ruling allows qualifying expats to receive 30% of their salary tax-free for up to 5 years, significantly reducing effective tax rates for highly skilled migrants."
      }
    }
  ]
}
</script>
{% endblock %}

{% block head %}
<style>
  .tax-bar { transition: width 0.6s ease-out; }
  .compare-col { min-width: 260px; }
  .country-check:checked + label { border-color: #6366f1; background: #eef2ff; }
  .dark .country-check:checked + label { border-color: #818cf8; background: rgba(99,102,241,0.15); }
  .toggle-track { transition: background-color 0.2s; }
  .toggle-thumb { transition: transform 0.2s; }
</style>
{% endblock %}

